info.name: Tumblr - Supernatural icon set
info.description: A set to replace the icons on your dashboard! The anti-possession tattoo, the Impala, the Colt, Ruby's knife, an angel-banishing sigil, and an angel feather! (Made to work with XKit!)
info.additionalInfo: Tested to work on Firefox only! Contact me on Tumblr (GeekintheJeep) with any questions/problems/requests.
